<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Data Deletion – FinFlow</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 820px;
      margin: 48px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 36px 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-top: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #2563eb;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .highlight {
      background: #f9fafb;
      border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .email-box {
      background: #eef2ff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: center;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.7rem;
      }

      .card {
        padding: 26px 22px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="container">
    <section class="card">
      <h1>Data Deletion Request</h1>
      <div class="subtitle">FinFlow Application</div>

      <p>
        FinFlow respects your privacy and gives you full control over your personal data. This page explains how you can request the deletion of your account and associated data.
      </p>

      <h2>What Data Will Be Deleted</h2>
      <p>Upon receiving and verifying your request, we will permanently delete the following data associated with your account:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Account information (such as registered email)</li>
        <li>Financial records, including transactions, budgets, and categories</li>
        <li>Any synchronized or backed-up data stored on our systems</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How to Request Data Deletion</h2>
      <p>
        To request deletion of your FinFlow account and data, please send an email using the information below:
      </p>

      <div class="highlight">
        <strong>Email Subject:</strong> Data Deletion Request – FinFlow<br /><br />
        <strong>Email Content:</strong><br />
        Please include the email address used to register your FinFlow account and clearly state that you are requesting permanent deletion of your account and all associated data.
      </div>

      <div class="email-box">
        Contact Email: ranzadev95@gmail.com
      </div>

      <h2>Important Notes</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Data deletion is permanent and cannot be undone</li>
        <li>Some minimal technical data may be retained temporarily if required by law or security obligations</li>
        <li>Requests are typically processed within a reasonable timeframe after verification</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Questions or Support</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions regarding data deletion or privacy practices, feel free to contact us using the email address above.
      </p>
    </section>

    <footer>
      © [Year] FinFlow. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
